title: BI Elite
description:
Power BI and DAX tips and tricks from a Microsoft Data Platform MVP. This channel is designed to teach you how to get the most out of Power BI and make you a super user in no time. So let's get started!

If you're new, check out the 3 Minute Tips or DAX for Power BI playlists. Make sure to leave a comment telling me what you'd like to see!

I look forward to connecting with you in the comments or by email!
